  <title>
    <phrase lang="cs">Vše</phrase>
    <phrase lang="en">Select All</phrase>
    <phrase lang="de">Alles</phrase>
    <phrase lang="fr">Tout</phrase>
    <phrase lang="it">Tutto</phrase>
    <phrase lang="no">Marker alt</phrase>
    <phrase lang="zh_CN">全选</phrase>
  </title>

  <indexterm lang="cs"><primary>Vše</primary></indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="de">
    <primary>Auswahl</primary>
    <secondary>Alles</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Selection</primary>
    <secondary> Select All</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="fr">
    <primary>Sélection</primary>
    <secondary>Tout sélectionner</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="it">
    <primary>Seleziona</primary>
    <secondary>Tutto</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="no">
    <primary>Marker</primary>
    <secondary>Alt</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="zh_CN"><primary>全部</primary></indexterm>


  <para lang="cs">
    Příkaz Vše vytvoří výběr zahrnující celou aktivní vrstvu.
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    Mit diesem Kommando können Sie eine Auswahl erstellen, welche die
    kompletten aktuelle Ebene umfasst.
  </para>
  <para lang="en">
    The <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem> command creates a new
    selection which contains everything on the current layer.
  </para>
  <para lang="fr">
    Tout sélectionner créera une nouvelle sélection comprenant l'ensemble du
    calque actif
  </para>
  <para lang="it">
    Il comando seleziona <guimenuitem>tutto</guimenuitem> crea una nuova
    selezione che contiene tutto il contenuto del livello corrente.
  </para>
  <para lang="no">
    Kommandoen <guimenuitem>Marker alt</guimenuitem> oppretter ei ny
    markering som inneheld alt på det aktive laget.
  </para>
  <para lang="zh_CN">
    全选命令创建一个包括活动图层上所有内容的选区。
  </para>


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activating the Command</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace dialogu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Aufruf des Kommandos</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Activer le Dialogue</phrase>
      <phrase lang="it">Attivazione del comando</phrase>
      <phrase lang="no">Aktivering</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">开启对话框</phrase>
    </title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang="cs">
          Tento příkaz je dostupný z nabídky obrázku jako
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Výběr</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Vše</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="en">
          You can access this command from the image menubar through
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>S</accel>elect</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>ll</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>,
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Der Menüeintrag kann aus dem Bildfenster
          erreicht werden:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>A</accel>uswahl</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>A</accel>lles</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          Cette commande se trouve dans
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>S</accel>élection</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>T</accel>out
            sélectionner</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
          et dans l'Éditeur de Sélection.
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          È possibile accedere a questo comando dalla barra del menu
          immagine tramite
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>S</accel>eleziona</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>T</accel>utto</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>,
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          Du får tilgang til denne undermenyen på biletmenyen via
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>Marker</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem>Alt</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang="zh_CN">
          该命令在<guimenuitem>图像&gt;选择/全部</guimenuitem>
        </para>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para lang="cs">
          Příkaz vše lze vyvolat i z klávesnice zkratkou
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
            <keycap>A</keycap>
          </keycombo>.
        </para>
        <para lang="en">
          or by using the keyboard shortcut
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
            <keycap>A</keycap>
          </keycombo>.
          You can also access it with the
          <link linkend="gimp-selection-dialog">Selection Editor</link>.
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Alternativ können Sie das Tastenkürzel
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Strg</keycap>
            <keycap>A</keycap>
          </keycombo>
          verwenden.
        </para>
        <para lang="fr">
          La combinaison de touches
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
            <keycap>A</keycap>
          </keycombo>
          activera la fonction Tout sélectionner.
        </para>
        <para lang="it">
          o usando la scorciatoia da tastiera
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap> <keycap>A</keycap> </keycombo>.  È
            possibile accedervi anche tramite l'<link
            linkend="gimp-selection-dialog">editor della selezione</link>.
        </para>
        <para lang="no">
          eller med snarvegen
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap> <keycap>A</keycap>
          </keycombo>.
        </para>
        <para lang="zh_CN">
          <keycombo>
            <keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
            <keycap>A</keycap>
          </keycombo>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem lang="no">  <!-- You can also access it with the... -->
        <para lang="no">
          Du har også tilgang via <!--PENDING:no <link
          linkend="gimp-selection-dialog"-->Markeringsbehandlaren<!--/link-->.
          </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
